Current working architecture for `rald`

lib/
  core/
    config/
      supabase_config.dart
    theme/
      app_theme.dart
  features/
    home/
      data/
        home_content.dart
      domain/
        entities/
          location_details.dart
      presentation/
        home_page.dart
        teaser_video_card.dart
        teaser_video_card_io.dart
        teaser_video_card_web.dart
        widgets/
          gallery_modal.dart
          gallery_tab.dart
          location_modal.dart
          wedding_background.dart
          wedding_navigation_rail.dart
          wedding_overlay.dart
    rsvp/
      data/
        datasources/
          rsvp_remote_data_source.dart
        repositories/
          rsvp_repository_impl.dart
      domain/
        entities/
          rsvp_submission.dart
        repositories/
          rsvp_repository.dart

Notes:
- `home_page.dart` is now only the screen composer.
- UI sections live in `presentation/widgets`.
- Static content for the home screen lives in `data/home_content.dart`.
- Supabase-ready boundaries live under `core/config` and `features/rsvp`.
